\begin_inset Formula $N_{\sigma}$
\end_inset

 is a unit normal of 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

, let 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

 be the map from 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 to the unit sphere 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{S}^{2}$
