 covered by the surface patch 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $G(P)=N_{P}\in\mathbf{S}^{2}$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $N_{P}$
\end_inset

 is the unit normal of 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

.
 Consider a tangent plane at 
\begin_inset Formula $P\in S$
\end_inset

.
